@startuml
title ATM Integrated State Machine

[*] --> Idle

' ===== STATES =====
state Idle
Idle : entry / Display Welcome

state "Waiting for PIN" as WaitingForPIN
state "Validating PIN" as ValidatingPIN
state "Waiting for Customer Choice" as WaitingForChoice
state "Processing Withdrawal" as ProcessingWithdrawal
state Dispensing
state Printing
state Ejecting
state Terminating
state Confiscating
state "Closed Down" as ClosedDown

ClosedDown : entry / Display System Down

' ===== MAIN FLOW =====
Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForPIN : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt

ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu
WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal Selected /\nRequest Withdrawal,\nDisplay Wait

ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved /\nDispense Cash,\nUpdate Status
Dispensing --> Printing : Cash Dispensed /\nPrint Receipt,\nDisplay Cash Dispensed,\nConfirm Cash Dispensed
Printing --> Ejecting : Receipt Printed /\nEject
Ejecting --> Terminating : Card Ejected /\nDisplay Ejected
Terminating --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Not Requested]

' ===== CANCEL / EJECT FROM MULTIPLE STATES =====
WaitingForPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

' ===== CONFISCATION LOGIC =====
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN / Confiscate
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Card Stolen, Card Expired /\nConfiscate, Update Status

Confiscating --> Terminating : Card Confiscated /\nDisplay Confiscated

' ===== FAILURE CASE =====
Dispensing --> ClosedDown : Insufficient Cash / Eject

@enduml